title: (Tues Full Show) Why Lunchbox Wanted To "Accidently" Key A Car + Bobby's Big Question He Wants To Ask A Psychic + We Play TV Show Finale
itunes:title: (Tues Full Show) Why Lunchbox Wanted To "Accidently" Key A Car + Bobby's Big Question He Wants To Ask A Psychic + We Play TV Show Finale
description:
Find out why Lunchbox wanted to "accidentally" key a car he saw this weekend. He was so proud of himself that he didn't, but we discuss if his reasoning why he even wanted to are justified. Plus, Amy's cousin who is a psychic is calling into the show tomorrow and Bobby wants to ask her a very important question, but it could lead to a bad answer. We go around the room and share why he should or shouldn't ask said question. Then, we play TV Show Finale with a listener who teams up with Amy as they try to guess which TV show finale we're talking about to win a prize.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
